{"id": 2319, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，手机内资料的整理 or 清理给你带来过哪些困扰？", "description": "换手机和手机号要下的决心快赶上改名字了。（题图来自：iStock © jossdim）", "record_count": 9520, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180503131710fnSLs6lBakJwEqXA.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-06T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4107, "title": "现如今，手机内资料的整理 or 清理给你带来过哪些困扰？", "content": "现如今，手机内资料的整理 or 清理给你带来过哪些困扰？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 279138, "content": "停机之后电商账号被手机号的新主人盗用买了东西", "image": "img/option/option/201805031619570ZevMG9r1qVnRXtc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 279139, "content": "想改密码发现注册时的手机号已经不用，没法收验证码", "image": "img/option/option/201805031620096QwGvlsYO0HngrFd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 279140, "content": "换手机的最大顾虑往往是“聊天记录能不能迁移”", "image": "img/option/option/20180503162018kBdcOZi7CD4toIGU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 279141, "content": "每个 app 里都有资料收藏，想找的时候根本记不住在哪", "image": "img/option/option/20180503162035ywfxQKvPo7mJNYal.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 279142, "content": "没有给微信联系人备注的习惯，换头像名字之后很难找", "image": "img/option/option/20180503163949QGAYc9pFKOMtgiv0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 279143, "content": "微信里只联系一次的联系人太多了，留着删了都不是", "image": "img/option/option/20180503162045EBOMueWJpXUFHYg1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 279144, "content": "手机 app 不知道咋分类，找不到完美的文件夹分配方式", "image": "img/option/option/20180503162605beQNpBHPJusvOzmL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 279145, "content": "每次换单位都需要重新调整社交网络可见分组", "image": "img/option/option/20180503162052meTPJn4tXi0uskva.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 279146, "content": "搬家忘改电商默认地址，还纳闷东西怎么收不到", "image": "img/option/option/20180503162101NoYvSCBbcUgnrR0E.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}